{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","data":{"fields":{"description":"## Why\nThe bot is being dropped; its code is the bug surface (15a1/0d3e/dc33). Deleting it is the resolution of those bugs.\n## What\n- [ ] Delete infra/autolander/ (loop.py, gerrit.py, failure.py, land.py, __init__.py) and tests/autolander/.\n- [ ] Remove the land / land-status CLI command + its wiring, and docs/land-contract.md.\n- [ ] Remove any imports/registry entries/refs to the above (grep sweep: autolander, land_contract, land-status).\n- [ ] Update the module-size allowlist / any config referencing infra/autolander.\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] No references to infra/autolander or the land command remain (grep clean).\n- [ ] make lint && make typecheck && make test green.\n- [ ] [operator-attested] Close bugs dc33, 15a1, 0d3e as obsolete — record the close-event IDs/timestamps as attestation on this ticket when this change lands (deleting the auto-lander code IS their resolution)."}},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"EDIT","timestamp":1783990182148229001,"uuid":"cf9a3eea-a50b-4c14-9d08-ae20dd17223e"}